        <title>Does Kicksecure block receiving connections via qvm-connect-tcp?</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Patrick]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Some Qubes RPC are blocked in Kicksecure sysmaint session.</p>
<aside class="onebox githubblob" data-onebox-src="https://github.com/Kicksecure/user-sysmaint-split/blob/master/usr/share/user-sysmaint-split/qubes-rpc-blocks">
