  </header>

  <article class="onebox-body">
    <h4><a href="https://github.com/Kicksecure/user-sysmaint-split/blob/master/usr/share/user-sysmaint-split/qubes-rpc-blocks" target="_blank" rel="noopener">usr/share/user-sysmaint-split/qubes-rpc-blocks</a></h4>

<div class="git-blob-info">
  <a href="https://github.com/Kicksecure/user-sysmaint-split/blob/master/usr/share/user-sysmaint-split/qubes-rpc-blocks" rel="noopener"><code>master</code></a>
</div>


      <pre><code class="lang-">qubes.OpenURL
qubes.TemplateDownload
qubes.PdfConvert
qubes.TemplateSearch
</code></pre>




  </article>

